观察¶

  • cap-shape: =b=c=x=f=k=s
  • cap-surface: =f=g=y=s
  • cap-color: =n=b=c=g=r=p=u=e=w=y
  • bruises: =t=f
  • odor: =a=1=c=y=f=m=n=p=s
  • gill-attachment: =a=d=f=n
  • gill-spacing: =c=w=d
  • gill-size: =b=n
  • gill-color: =k=n=b=h=g=r=o=p=u=e=w=y
  • stalk-shape: =e=t
  • stalk-root: -=b=c=u=e=z=r=
  • stalk-surface-above-ring: =f=y=k=s
  • stalk-surface-below-ring: =f=y=k=s
  • stalk-color-above-ring: =nBUff=b=c=g=o=p=e=w=y
  • stalk-color-below-ring: =n=b=c=g=o=p=e=w=y
  • veil-type: =p=u
  • veil-color: =n=o=w=y
  • ring-number: 0=n1=o2=t
  • ring-type: cobwebby=c=eflling=f=lnone=n=p=szone=z
  • spore-print-color: =k=n=b=h=r=o=u=w=y
  • population: =a=c=n=s=v=y
  • habitat: =g=1=m=p=u=w=d

In [35]:
import time
from sklearn.metrics import silhouette_score
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans

def cluster(X):
    '''
    K-Means
    
    
        X
    
        best_clusters
        score
        
    '''
    score = -1
    duration = 0
    start = time.time()
    # K215
    for clusters_num in range(2, 15):  
        # TODO
        # kmeansclusters_num
        kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=clusters_num)
        
        # TODO
        # kmeansXXtest_preds

        test_preds = kmeans.fit_predict(X)

        # TODO
        # silhouette_scoretest_score
        test_score = silhouette_score(X,test_preds)
        
        # 
        print("component score is ", test_score)

        #
        if (score < test_score):
            best_clustersnum = clusters_num
            score = test_score
            best_clusters=kmeans

    # 
    end = time.time()      
    duration += end - start

    # 
    print(': {:.4f}s'.format(duration))
    print('k{}{:.3f}'.format(best_clustersnum, score))
    
    return best_clusters, score

# clusterdata
clu, score = cluster(data)
